languages.text: {n}Октавиана мрачно пожимает плечами.{/n} "Не знаю, нужен ли еще Футфолу "Амасекус". Видимо, скоро придется закрыть его и начать какое-то новое предприятие. Но блюстители нас больше не трогают — проблемой был Владайм, забывший, что он является контрабандистом, и начавший играть в бунтовщика".

{n}Octaviana shrugs sullenly.{/n} "I don't know if Footfall even needs the Amasecus anymore. I might have to close up shop and start some new business. But the enforcers don't bother us anymore — Vladaym was the problem. He forgot he was a smuggler and started playing the rebel."

languages.text: {n}オクタヴィアナは不機嫌そうに肩をすくめる。{/n}「フットフォールにはもうアマセックは必要ないのかもしれないわ。店を閉じて新しい仕事を始めた方ががいいのかも。でも、もうエンフォーサーに悩まされることもなくなりましたし。ヴラダイムは厄介だったから。自分が密輸業者であることも忘れて、反乱ごっこを始めるなんて」

languages.text: {n}Octaviana hausse les épaules, l'air maussade.{/n} « Je ne sais même pas si Castel a encore besoin de l'Amasecus. Je vais peut-être devoir fermer boutique et me lancer dans autre chose. Au moins, les prévôts ne nous embêtent plus ; c'était Vladaym, le problème. Il avait oublié qu'il avait lui aussi été contrebandier et il s'était mis à jouer les rebelles. »
languages.original_text: {n}Octaviana shrugs sullenly.{/n} "I don't know if Footfall even needs the Amasecus anymore. I might have to close up shop and start some new business. But the enforcers don't bother us anymore — Vladaym was the problem. He forgot he was a smuggler and started playing the rebel."

languages.text: {n}奥克塔维娜闷闷不乐地耸了耸肩。{/n}“我不知道落脚港还需不需要烈酒修会了。我感觉我可能得关门大吉，另起炉灶了。不过，那些执法者已经不再骚扰我们了，他们所有的目光都放在了弗拉迪姆身上。那个人已经忘了自己只是个走私贩子，开始扮演起反抗军的角色了。”

languages.text: {n}Octaviana zuckt mürrisch mit den Schultern.{/n} "Ich weiß gar nicht, ob Footfall das Amasecus überhaupt noch braucht. Vielleicht muss ich den Laden schließen und etwas Neues eröffnen. Immerhin stören uns die Enforcers nicht länger – das Problem war Vladaym. Er hatte vergessen, dass er ein Schmuggler war, und begann, den Rebellen zu spielen."

languages.text: {n}Octaviana se encoge de hombros, malhumorada.{/n} «No sé si la gente de Paso sigue necesitando el Amasecus. Puede que tenga que cerrar y abrir otro negocio. Al menos el personal de seguridad ya no nos molesta más. El problema era Vladaym: olvidó su papel de contrabandista y se hizo el rebelde».

languages.text: {n}Octaviana somurtarak omuz silkiyor.{/n} "Binliman'da artık Amasekus'a lüzum olur mu, emin değilim. Kepenkleri kapatıp yeni iş kurmak zorunda kalabilirim. Gerçi infazcılar artık bize bulaşmıyor. Sıkıntı, Vladaym yüzündendi. Herif, kaçakçı olduğunu unutup isyancılığa soyunmuştu."

But the enforcers don't bother us anymore — Vladaym was the problem. He forgot he was a smuggler and started playing the rebel."

traits.locale_text: {n}Octaviana somurtarak omuz silkiyor.{/n} "Binliman'da artık Amasekus'a lüzum var mı, ondan emin değilim. Belki de kepenkleri kapatıp başka bir işe geçerim. Gerçi infazcılar artık bizi rahatsız etmiyor... Sıkıntı, Vladaym yüzündendi. Herif kaçakçı olduğunu unutmuş, isyancı olduğunu sanmaya başlamıştı."
